# Phase 7.2: the on-disk catalog (branches/, goals/, nodes/) is
# intentionally NOT ignored. Those YAML files are the canonical
# shared state per PLAN.md "GitHub as the canonical shared state";
# each user clones + pulls + PRs contributions through those dirs.
# The SqliteCached backend mirrors to SQLite alongside the YAML
# write, but the .db file is excluded via `*.db` above — only the
# YAML is committed.

